	measure 在範圍內 = VAR sel=[_選月數] VAR d=[_最新期] VAR cutoff=IF(sel>=9999, DATE(1900,1,1), EDATE(d, -MIN(sel,240))) RETURN IF(MAX(fact_price_history[period_date]) > cutoff, 1, 0)
		isHidden
		lineageTag: e6861b8e-f0b8-46a6-893b-019f61bf42ad

